app.boxmate

Class Showing

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.boxmate.Showing

  • public class Showing
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents a showing of a show (i.e. if the show is being played more than once). UPDATES: June 12: - Now using custom date/time classes.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.0 (24/05/2012)
    Author:
    Jonathan Tan
